description: At the end of Cabo part 5, Sgt. Major takes Darling miles away from the villa and into the Mexican heat for training. Darling has a grueling day in the rough hills of Mexico. She is tickled, fucked, bound, fingered, flogged, dragged, frog-marched, fucked till orgasm, and generally has a tough time of it Hogtied style. In the end she is returned to the Villa with just a little better attitude than when she left.If you missed Cabo 1-5 scroll down and watch them; it sets up the entire fantasy we have laid before you.
title: Cabo, the Return. Part 6
